description:
This is a 11 minute workout called '60-Second Intervals Row' from the channel Buffy Williams.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The The Firestarter vibe means Fast, explosive, and electrifying. Short but devastating. This is especially good for When you only have 10-20 minutes but want to give 1000%. The The Endorphin Wave vibe means Elevated energy, feel-good movement, steady build. This is especially good for When you want a challenging but steady burn..
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Extreme and Challenging.

Original workout description: Ready to rev your engine? Look no further as you and Buffy tackle 60-second intervals. 

Max rhythm: 28, Format: HIIT...
